&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;https://www.quora.com/Which-HTTP-code-is-best-suited-for-validation-errors-400-or-422&#34;&gt;Which HTTP code is best suited for validation errors: 400 or 422? - Quora&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
